<HEADLINE> Sweden Names New Coach </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, October 13 (Xinhua) -- Swedish Tommy Soderberg
Monday took the occupation as the national soccer coach after
Tommy Svensson's leaving.
</P>
