Sectors which have benefited from Dutch aid cover agriculture,
especially livestock and cooperatives, health, education, water and
environment, it added.
</P>
<P>
During his tour, the prime minister will make trips to Dutch
financed projects in Arusha and Kagera regions and refugee camps in
the Kigoma region.
</P>
<P>
The Netherlands has also given assistance to the Tanzanian
government to help mitigate the negative impact of refugee influx on
the local population.
</P>
<P>
A rural program is also being implemented in 11 districts in the
east African country under Dutch aid, the statement said. 
