ensure that 1994 Lusaka Peace Protocol be fully implemented.
</P>
<P>
Hare said that U.S. government would continue to aid the
Angolan government for a final peace in the country.
</P>
<P>
Hare arrived in Luanda today for his five-day visit to meet
various sides of the peace process and get the latest information
on the development of the peace process in the country. 
