<HEADLINE> EC Approves Humanitarian Aid for Afghanistan, Laos </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BRUSSELS, October 14 (Xinhua) -- The European Commission, the
European Union's (EU) executive body, has approved a package of
humanitarian aid worth two million ECUs (2.5 million U.S.
dollars) for Afghanistan and Laos.
</P>
<P>
The money for Afghanistan is to be spent on shelter, food and
medical aid, especially in the capital Kabul, said a press release
here today.
</P>
