in the world with four Olympic table tennis golds in the last two
Olympics.
</P>
<P>
"She has won all but a mixed doubles in the Olympics," Xu said.
"She is awaiting the chance."
</P>
<P>
Table tennis has four official Olympic events of both men's and
women's singles and doubles. 
