century was the topic of a discussion at a symposium that opened
here today.
</P>
<P>
It was the first meeting of its kind for the world's
telecommunications industry, and the first international
telecommunications symposium sponsored by Beijing.
</P>
<P>
Senior managers of the top telecommunications companies from
the U.S., Britain, France, and Germany, and other countries were
present, as well as experts from the cities of Beijing, Shanghai,
Tianjin, and Chongqing, and from Guangdong, Fujian, and Jiangsu
provinces.
</P>
