The participants exchanged views on the role of
telecommunications in economic expansion and how to meet new
telecommunications challenges in the 21st century.
</P>
<P>
Ni Yilin, director of the Beijing Telecommunications
Administration, said that the integration of global
telecommunications is apparent and the symposium is bound to
promote Beijing's fledgling industry.
</P>
<P>
Beijing has a combined capacity of five million
telephone lines; the number of subscribers has reached 2.4
million.  
