retirement medical insurance, were bound by government policy
and could not be granted immediately.
</P>
<P>
The workers demands include confirming jobs pending appointments
as permanent staff, calculating bonuses, increasing education
allowances by 30 percent and providing advances to pay tuition
fees. 
