Madeleine Albright and Venezuelan Foreign Minister Miguel Angel
Burelli Rivas to strengthen a "strategic alliance" against illegal
drugs.
</P>
<P>
The United States agreed to provide Venezuela 11.5 million
dollars in aid.
</P>
<P>
Clinton arrived in Venezuela Sunday to start a 24-hour
visit. Venezuela is the first stop of Clinton's first South
America tour which will also take him to Brazil and Argentina.
